    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Oil derived from the nuts of the tree Aleurites cordata. It does not gelatinize when heated and is used for varnishes, waterproofing, paper and soaps.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
